org.lightningj.paywall.btcpayserver.vo

Class Invoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lightningj.paywall.JSONParsable
      • org.lightningj.paywall.btcpayserver.vo.Invoice

  • public class Invoice
extends JSONParsable
    Value object representing one BTC Pay Server JSON invoice. Doesn't implement the full API just the necessary parts to integrate with paywall-core requirements. Created by philip on 2018-10-17.
